data.app-config.production.yaml:
app:
  title: Kaos Backstage
  # Tu IP publica y puerto externo
  baseUrl: http://83.32.50.24:8082

backend:
  baseUrl: http://83.32.50.24:8082
  listen: 0.0.0.0:7007
  auth:
    keys:
      - secret: "secret"
  csp:
    upgradeInsecureRequests: false
  
  cors:
    origin: http://83.32.50.24:8082
    methods: [GET, HEAD, PATCH, POST, PUT, DELETE]
    credentials: true
  database:
    client: pg
    connection:
      host: postgresql
      port: 5432
      user: backstage
      password: backstage

auth:
  environment: production
  providers:
    guest:
      dangerouslyAllowOutsideDevelopment: true
    github:
      development:
        clientId: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID}
        clientSecret: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET}
      production:
        clientId: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID}
        clientSecret: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET}
